<Paragraph>
<Bold>Essential XlsIO</Bold> supports creating macro files from scratch programmatically. This sample demonstrates the creation of Excel charts from macro code in different formats like Excel 97-2003, macro-enabled Excel template and macro-enabled Excel workbook.
</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List> 
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>
Create Excel chart from macro code for the data provided in the Excel workbook.
</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>
Save the macro-enabled file in various file formats (XLS, XLSM, XLTM).
</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
